 their Adjudication unit is undergoing transitional changes and the Adjudic=
ation process will follow in due course (up to 2-months). It has become app=
arent that CSOS is unable to expeditiously resolve these cases.<br>
</p>
<p style=3D"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br>
</p>
<p style=3D"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><u>Legal </u>- No debtors=
 have adhered to their payment arrangements or signed Acknowledgment of Deb=
t. The decision has therefore been made to hand over the following units to=
 BBM Law who specialise in arrear
 levy collections:</p>
<ul>
<li>TV2 (Mphiyakhe) - will not increase payment; balance outstanding increa=
sing.<br>
</li><li>TV3 (Bahyi) - paid minimal amounts then nothing since Jan; not res=
ponding to contact efforts.<br>
</li><li>TV5 (Fick) - unable to contact; no payments on record.<br>
</li><li>TV9 &amp; TV13 (Motsoagae) - making monthly payments of R750 for e=
ach unit; arrears increasing; not responding to contact efforts.<br>
</li><li>TV15 (Alemeida / Da Silva) - Monthly payments of R2,000 does not c=
over levies and charges; needs to increase payment amount; unable to contac=
t.<br>
</li></ul>
<p style=3D"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">In brief, a (registered) =
Letter of Demand will now be sent / served by the Sheriff. If no response f=
rom the debtors, a formal Summons will be issued and served again by the Sh=
eriff. If owners do not defend, we
 will apply for Default Judgement which vastly affects the creditworthiness=
 of the debtor. It is at this stage that debtors are most likely to adhere =
to formal payment arrangements to avoid Warrants of Execution where movable=
 assets are sold in auction. However,
 the final stage would be Section 66 where the property is sold to recover =
the debt owed to the BC.<br>
</p>
<p style=3D"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br>
</p>
<p style=3D"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><b>We look forward to you=
r feedback and suggestions to address the above management issues.</b><br>
</p>
<p style=3D"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br>
</p>
<p style=3D"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">Kind regards,</p>
<p style=3D"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">Nancy<br>
</p>
